                     <interp inst="t18320906-208-person1735" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I found the prisoner in the watch-house. I have the three sovereigns, and 5 1/2d., which I found in his pocket.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I came out of his shop, and shut the door; I proceeded fifty yards, and heard a cry of Stop thief! - seeing a man run, I ran after him, and by St. Dunstan's church, I stopped, seeing I was pursued.</p>
